{"tid":802550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州讀書的許小姐: 有了身份證(內地居住證)後，我相信會很方便。","createTime":"2018-09-01T14:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T09:12:29.000Z","uid":112551,"like":556,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"3f34e73da5bf7ddbe2e8aa93a2c82fbfe333c83d","tid":802550,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/215548_aeeeb48c5c1152d7ac534c4556435b7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F215548_aeeeb48c5c1152d7ac534c4556435b7f.png&h=655a5469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在廣州讀書的許小姐表示，居住證方便求職。暨南大學新聞與傳播研究生許小姐說道：「我原本在內地想做兼職，但當時他們說，香港人身份證跟我們不太一樣，他們會有些麻煩，甚至他們說，我們不知如何幫你申請。有了身份證(居住證)後，我相信會很方便。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b8a4e95e603832361e89674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5b8a4e95e603832361e89674%2F&d=RJHxuIpf0Lrhs%2BOy1BKjO26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=89dc58ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b8a4e95e603832361e89674/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌，居然仲想起強國做兼職，無錢仲學人翻強國讀書，使唔使窮到咁丫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要起強國讀研究生，人地入港三大Master洗底，佢就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"aeee393bba1b2af55f9261419fc7337809826b01","tid":802550,"uid":198583,"like":4,"dislike":122,"score":-118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"想屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8e90f538d536c9e835bb87c9137174b54cd0d5","tid":802550,"uid":79563,"like":258,"dislike":6,"score":252,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"做100%支那MK最方便<br />\n<br />\n咁方便就唔好返黎香港啦<br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該修例, 同時取消佢地身份證"},{"pid":"ff9d8813fb943b31860d60eef314aec462fd2cba","tid":802550,"uid":7631